NK036(chi)019:0: bsam gtan mig gi sgron ma bzhugs so h+aum rag
NK036(chi)019:1: rig rdo rje sems dpa' lu gu rgyud kyi sku
NK036(chi)019:2: la phyag 'tshal lo e ma sangs rgyas 'bras bu
NK036(chi)019:3: tshe 'dir bsgrub pa yis skal ldan snying po don
NK036(chi)019:4: du gnyer ba des chos nyid mngon sum gnad la
NK036(chi)019:5: 'bebs pa'i phyir spyod pa'i gnad du 'khor 'das ru
NK036(chi)019:6: shan dbye dur khrod lung stong dag tu rgyu bar
NK036(chi)019:7: bya bsgom pa'i gnad du 'dug stangs rnam gsum bstan
NK036(chi)019:8: lus ngag yid gsum dal bar rab tu gces lta
NK036(chi)019:9: ba'i gnad du mi 'gul gzer gsum gdab lu gu
NK036(chi)019:10: rgyud la rtag tu 'dris par bya mig gi gsal
NK036(chi)019:11: byed sman sbyar sngags pu dzahh+aum nyid bsgrang chos nyag
NK036(chi)019:12: gcig kyi sku dang dbang po mig zhal mjal bas
NK036(chi)019:13: rig pa tshad phebs 'khrul snang sangs rgyas te phung
NK036(chi)019:14: po lhag med stong gsum 'jas bkang nas mthong thos
NK036(chi)019:15: thams cad 'khor ba phyir bsnyil cing lhun grub sa
NK036(chi)019:16: la kun tu bzang por gyur bdag 'dra bye ma
NK036(chi)019:17: mu tra nyid kyis kyang phyi nang gsang ba bla
NK036(chi)019:18: med mchog nyid kyis yang gsang snying gi thabs mchog
NK036(chi)019:19: rnams la 'bad rig 'dzin chen por 'gyur ro phyi
NK036(chi)019:20: rabs snying bu rnams de la dang po nas yo
NK036(chi)019:21: gi'i mig gsal bar bya ba'i phyir mig bsro zhing
NK036(chi)019:22: bku mnye bya mig shed bskyed cing gsal ba la
NK036(chi)019:23: a ru ra rgya gar ma go snyod r+ts+aa a
NK036(chi)019:24: wa dang sngo rtag tu ngu sbrul sha rnams rtsi
NK036(chi)019:25: bzhin btags te sbrang rtsi dang sbyar nas lto stong
NK036(chi)019:26: la dum re zos nas mig shed che zhing rig
NK036(chi)019:27: pa lu gu rgyud gsal bar 'gyur ro yang 'o
NK036(chi)019:28: ma dang skyer pa'i bar shun gyi khan+da dang gzi
NK036(chi)019:29: nag khra rnying pa brdungs pa'i phye ma dang bya
NK036(chi)019:30: nag mo'i sgo nga'i ser mo dang bzhi sbyar te
NK036(chi)019:31: tshes gcig dang gnam stong dang nya'i nyin par tho
NK036(chi)019:32: rangs kha sngon du chu grang mos mig dang gdong
NK036(chi)019:33: dag par bkrus te de nas de kun lde gus
NK036(chi)019:34: mig la bkus nas de nangs par bzhin ba ser
NK036(chi)019:35: mo'i 'o ma bkol ba'i nang du shing mngar btab
NK036(chi)019:36: ste 'a thung na mig 'grib par mi 'gyur zhing
NK036(chi)019:37: rig pa la lu gu rgyud gsal lo rdo sbur
NK036(chi)019:38: len rtsi bzhin btags la sbrang dkar dang sbyar nas
NK036(chi)019:39: mig la byugs na skya rib sel bar 'gyur ro
NK036(chi)019:40: yang shel dang thod le kor dang ga pur dang
NK036(chi)019:41: gla rtsi rnams rtsi bzhin sbyangs la bu khye'u 'thung
NK036(chi)019:42: ba'i 'o ma dang sbyar la mig la byugs na
NK036(chi)019:43: rig pa lu gu rgyud gsal bar 'gyur ro yang
NK036(chi)019:44: snan smug po sbal rgyab dang ram rtsa skam po
NK036(chi)019:45: dang zhun thig le dang sag ram tsi dang de
NK036(chi)019:46: rnams rtsi bzhin btags te bu 'thung ba'i 'o ma
NK036(chi)019:47: dang sbyar la mig la yang yang byugs na zhag
NK036(chi)019:48: bdun na mig 'grib pa phyed de rig pa rdo
NK036(chi)019:49: rje lu gu rgyud gsal lo yang rag thal dang
NK036(chi)019:50: thod le kor dang gnyis zhib par byas te 'o
NK036(chi)019:51: spris dang sbyar te mig la byugs na skam tshag
NK036(chi)019:52: dang dmar tshig dang skya rib sos te rig pa
NK036(chi)019:53: gsal lo dgongs mo lte khung du mar byugs kyin
NK036(chi)019:54: mnyes na mig skam tshag dang mchu rengs pa sos
NK036(chi)019:55: so yang go snyod dang gla rtsi'i chus dgongs mo
NK036(chi)019:56: lte khung du byugs na mig gsal zhing gangs la
NK036(chi)019:57: phyin kyang phyid par mi 'gyur ro dus rgyun du
NK036(chi)019:58: zhogs par rlung bzung ste lag mthil gnyis kyis mig
NK036(chi)019:59: gnyis drag par 'phur nas chu gtsang mas khrus byas
NK036(chi)019:60: na mig gi sgrib sha bcad cing bkrus pa zhes
NK036(chi)019:61: bya ste skya rib mi 'byung zhing gsal bar 'gyur
NK036(chi)019:62: ro yang mig la sha 'dzer byung na lto stong
NK036(chi)019:63: la zan dron mo dum gcig gi nang du mar
NK036(chi)019:64: dum gcig bcug ste de'i rlangs pa mig na ba
NK036(chi)019:65: la bdug la ngag tu srin long bya ba nyi
NK036(chi)019:66: shu rtsagaciga byas te khar bcug na sos par 'gyur
NK036(chi)019:67: ro yang mig la ling thog byung na gla rtsi
NK036(chi)019:68: ka ra cu gang zhun thig le rnams rtsi bzhin
NK036(chi)019:69: byas te mig la zi tsam re gdab sngags 'di
NK036(chi)019:70: ci mang du bzlas te phug ron gyi dang ru'i
NK036(chi)019:71: rtse mos lce rtse nas blangs la mig la blan
NK036(chi)019:72: pas sos par 'gyur ro lhing lhing thog thog a
NK036(chi)019:73: tsi li s+w+aa h+aa yang mig tu rdul dang gra
NK036(chi)019:74: ma song na sngags 'dis phyin par 'gyur ro ya
NK036(chi)019:75: ma dan ting s+w+aa h+aa yang dus gnyen po'i dus
NK036(chi)019:76: su mig la zan bsgres la brgya rtsa gcig btang
NK036(chi)019:77: na mig long bar mi 'gyur ro yang rtsa a
NK036(chi)019:78: ba dang cong zhi dang brag zhun dang sbrul sngon
NK036(chi)019:79: po'i sha dang 'bras bu gsum dang dom mkhris dang
NK036(chi)019:80: khyi nag po'i mkhris pa spre'u'i mkhris pa rta nag
NK036(chi)019:81: po'i mkhris pa mi'i mkhris pa 'ug pa'i mkhris pa
NK036(chi)019:82: sngo rtag tu ngu de rnams sbrang rtsi dang sbyar
NK036(chi)019:83: te lto stong la zla ba gsum zos na sha'i
NK036(chi)019:84: spyan dang ldan cing rig pa rdo rje lu gu
NK036(chi)019:85: rgyud gsal bar 'gyur ro yang srin bu me khyer
NK036(chi)019:86: dang lhang ma lhang tsher dang de mo nag mo'i
NK036(chi)019:87: sgo nga dang sbyar la mig gi steng du blan
NK036(chi)019:88: cing phyin na 'od sna tshogs pa 'char bar 'gyur
NK036(chi)019:89: nges so sngags 'di yang 'bum tsho'am ci mang du
NK036(chi)019:90: yi dam byas te bzlas na 'od kor phor pa
NK036(chi)019:91: tsam du 'phel bar 'gyur ro chen kong chen b+ha
NK036(chi)019:92: ha na zhun chen zhu ha na g+ha mi ston
NK036(chi)019:93: yam des ni ye shes kyi spyan gsal zhing rgyas
NK036(chi)019:94: par 'gyur ro rtsa lam thams cad byang zhing rig
NK036(chi)019:95: pa 'phel bar 'gyur ro lar mig la phan pa'i
NK036(chi)019:96: sman rnams sbyar zhing sngags la yang 'bad par bya'o
NK036(chi)019:97: man shel dang rin chen dang s+aur+ya dang tsan+d+ra dang
NK036(chi)019:98: +aa lo ke thabs sna tshogs la bslab cing rig
NK036(chi)019:99: pa dngos kyi 'phel rtsi bar bya'o //
NK036(chi)019:100: kye ma rig pa dngos nyid lta ba'i skyes bu
NK036(chi)019:101: rnams sgron gsal man ngag 'di la nan tan mdzod
NK036(chi)019:102: dngoos po gshis kyi gnas lugs lu gu rgyud 'di
NK036(chi)019:103: las chos gzhan yod re na ra kan byas chos
NK036(chi)019:104: tshe 'dir shor ba'i gang zag rnams byar med gnas
NK036(chi)019:105: lugs bltas na mi legs sam 'di med chos la
NK036(chi)019:106: 'bungs kyang sangs rgyas ring de phyir nyag gcig bsgoms
NK036(chi)019:107: na mi legs sam rig 'dzin lhag med 'grub pa
NK036(chi)019:108: rnams dang ni dbyer med gcig tu bsres na mi
NK036(chi)019:109: legs sam dus gsum sangs rgyas 'di dang zhal mjal
NK036(chi)019:110: nas 'bras bu phyi dus re bas ga nas 'ong
NK036(chi)019:111: zag bcas sgyu lus khol po gtan mi nus rdos
NK036(chi)019:112: bcas da res chod cig srin bu tsho bsam gtan
NK036(chi)019:113: mig gi sgron ma zhes bya ba pan+di ta chen
NK036(chi)019:114: po bi ma la mi tras mdzad pa rdzogs so
NK036(chi)019:115: rgya rgya rgya kha tham bla ma dam pa ku
NK036(chi)019:116: ma r+aa dza'i gdams pa byar med klong yangs kyi
NK036(chi)019:117: rnal 'byor pa klong chen rab 'byams kyis nan tan
NK036(chi)019:118: du zhus pa +thii rgya rgya rgya /
